notes.title: Kill Master Windu
notes.text: I've always been envious of that purple light saber, would be cool if I could get rid of that in the process

notes.title: Submit to Darth Sidious
notes.text: Weird how close that name is to insidious.

notes.title: Cleanse the Temple
notes.text: Too many damn younglings... there's probably something I could do about that.

notes.title: Go to Mustafar
notes.text: Some, like me, like it hot.

notes.title: Burn Limbs off
notes.text: Enough with the rest of the fleshy ones, my robot one is the best!

notes.title: Eradicate Resistance
notes.text: My way or the highway (but really just my way)
